These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
House: futuristic, wooden, cottage, ranch-style
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family, mystery
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dannemann, pall-mall, baccarat
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, motorbike, taxi
 1. the dannemann-smoker is not to the right of the bongani-smoker##8
 2. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the bongani-smoker is not to the left of the baccarat-smoker##8
 5. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 7. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the person driving the jet-ski and the dannemann-smoker##2
 9. the person driving the taxi is the person watching family movies##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
11. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
13. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
14. the wooden house is the person driving the motorbike##1
15. the wooden house is not the dannemann-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| House         | futuristic     | wooden   | ranch-style | cottage |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| Cigar         | dannemann  | pall-mall  | baccarat  | bongani |
| Transport     | airplane    | motorbike | jet-ski     | taxi    |

