The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the fan of salsa is between the owner of the dog and the fan of indie##2
 2. the person driving the skateboard is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
 4. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the owner of the frog##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaisy##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
17. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person who growsdaisy is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
