There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, juice, hot-chocolate
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 5. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the person playing go##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
 7. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 9. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
11. the person playing go is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
12. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
